Eh. Not so sure about it. When I want my pet to deal damage, I'll have my water pet up and to the mobs back. I ussually get very decent dps when I do that. I am more concerned really with pet survivability. Dps in my view just falls short of that.
<br />

<br />
Comment on half pet/half nuke damage
<br />

<br />
I guess I am just in the pool that likes seeing half of my damage comes from my pet and half comes from me. I will look at some figures on the board and see what it truely is, but I do think the pet's dps is a little bit better than 3:1. On raiding mobs this is very true. Otherwise I don't know.
<br />

<br />
Keep the suggestions coming!</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
